 Create basic Layout component (SEO, Metadata)
 Implement responsive Navigation Bar (Glassmorphism)
 Implement Footer
 Create 3D Canvas wrapper / Background component
 Hero Section

 Implement Hero container and text content
 Create 3D Avatar/Abstract floating element
 Add cycling subtitle animation
 About Section

 Build About geometry/layout
 Add floating specific cards (Problem solving, DSA, etc.)
 Skills Section

 Create 3D Orbit/Card layout for skills
 Map skills (Frontend, Backend, Blockchain, Tools)
 Projects Section

 Design interactive 3D Project Cards
 Implement hover effects and external links
 Experience Section

 Build Vertical 3D Timeline component
 Add animation on scroll
 Contact Section

 Create Contact Form with 3D elements
 detailed social links
 Polish & Optimization

 Ensure Mobile Responsiveness
 SEO Optimization (Check meta tags, lighthouse)
